Globalisation means that the tax decisions of one country can have a major effect on other countries.
More coordinated and ambitious EU action would ensure a fairer tax environment for all. #QualifiedMajority #FairTaxation https://t.co/efYkpFw1RL

EU countries would no longer have to reduce taxation on large companies to remain competitive, lightening the heavy tax burden currently felt by workers, consumers, and small domestic companies. #QualifiedMajority #FairTaxation https://t.co/1wS66JnjJf

Key proposals for growth and competitiveness have been blocked for years due to the unanimity rule.
#QualifiedMajority for taxation would make the #SingleMarket stronger, support businesses and attract investors. https://t.co/mPPvoA02oo

Billions are lost every year due to VAT fraud and tax avoidance.
Better cooperation between EU countries would help them recoup these huge losses. #QualifiedMajority https://t.co/Yfv2rdnzUj

With #QualifiedMajority, the EU would better match their expectations, thanks to quicker and more effective decisions. https://t.co/jKQP3fGpqW

Our efforts to disembark the migrants on boats in Malta have brought results. 
All those on board are being disembarked right now. 
We commend Malta for allowing this disembarkation and EU countries that showed active solidarity in accepting them. @Avramopoulos on #migrationEU https://t.co/O4ZuRK5zqE

With over €370 billion mobilised, the #JunckerPlan is both a success and a beginning: more #InvestEU opportunities lie ahead with our target of €500 billion  investment by 2020. 
Learn more about #EFSI → https://t.co/4o9bxfzX2U https://t.co/xvfotmuPxt

The euro area unemployment rate was 7.9% in November 2018, down from 8.7% in November 2017. This is the lowest rate recorded since October 2008.

The EU28 unemployment rate was 6.7%. This remains the lowest rate since January 2000.

More @EU_Eurostat → https://t.co/3aqKPQVJtG https://t.co/j3Dab9jpvq

No foreign exchange costs, more choice, better prices. The euro makes it easy to... SHOP 🛍️. Today the € is the currency of 19 EU countries 🇪🇺. It makes it easier and cheaper to compare prices and shop abroad → https://t.co/PVMl8scnpv #EUROat20 https://t.co/r9p00EmoGo
